11 Sec. 31518a. (1) An owner shall submit to the department a
12 comprehensive evaluation report prepared by a licensed professional
13 engineer that evaluates the overall safety of the dam. The
14 comprehensive evaluation report must be submitted not less than
15 once every 10 years on a schedule determined by the department.
16 (2) The comprehensive evaluation report must include, but is
17 not limited to, a detailed evaluation and recommendation for all of
18 the following:
