20 adequacy, and structural integrity.
21 (b) The adequacy of the dam's original design and
22 construction.
23 (c) The adequacy of the dam's operation and maintenance
24 procedures.
25 (d) Probable failure modes and risk reduction measures.
26 (e) Conformance with current dam safety practices.
27 (f) Any deficiencies that exist that could lead to failure of
28 the dam.
29 (g) Maintenance, repair, and alterations of a dam that are
