20 Sec. 31518c. An owner shall prepare, and keep current, an
21 operation and maintenance plan and submit the plan to the
22 department for review. An operation and maintenance plan must
23 include all of the following information:
24 (a) A description of the dam.
25 (b) Contact information for the dam owner and any agent or
