9 Sec. 31518d. (1) An owner shall prepare and keep current a
10 safety and security plan and submit the plan to the department for
11 review. A safety and security plan must include all of the
12 following information:
13 (a) A summary of all physical safety measures at the dam,
14 including any signage, waterway barriers, safety fencing, railings,
15 or other safety devices.
16 (b) A summary of all physical security measures at the dam,
17 including security cameras, alarms, security fencing, gates, doors,
18 barriers, or other security devices.
