22 (ii) Notification flow charts and call lists.
23 (iii) Response procedures.
24 (iv) A safety and security incident report template.
25 (2) The owner shall notify the department of any safety or
26 security incidents within 24 hours after the incident occurs.
27 Sec. 31520. (1) The owner or his or her agent shall advise the
28 department and the affected off-site public authorities and safety
29 agencies of any sudden or unprecedented flood or unusual or
